<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Boholina reducta sp. nov., holotype female. A antennule B antenna (arrow indicating small serrated process) C mandible. Scale bars: 100 µm." , "Figure 4. Boholina reducta sp. nov., holotype female. A maxillula B maxilla C maxilliped. Scale bar: 100 µm." , "Figure 9. Boholina reducta sp. nov., SEM micrographs A-D female E-F male A distal spines of P 4 Exp- 3 B rostrum, ventral view (arrow indicating tip of rostrum) C genital double-somite, ventral view (arrow indicating sensilla near gonopores) D gonopores, latero-ventral view (arrow indicating sensilla near gonopores) E P 5, posterior F P 5, anterior. Abbreviations: gp, gonoporal plates; gs, gonoporal slits." , "Figure 6. Boholina reducta sp. nov., allotype male. A habitus, dorsal view B habitus, lateral view C urosome, dorsal view. Scale bars: 100 µm." , "Figure 8. Boholina reducta sp. nov., SEM micrographs, female. A distal segment of antennary endopod B mandibular palp C maxillula D maxilla E maxilliped F P 5, posterior." , "Figure 2. Boholina reducta sp. nov., holotype female. A habitus, dorsal view B habitus, lateral view (arrow indicating tip of rostrum) C rostrum, ventral view (arrow indicating tip of rostrum) D urosome, ventral view (arrow indicating sensilla near gonopores). Scale bars: 100 µm." , "Figure 5. Boholina reducta sp. nov. A - E holotype female, F paratype female. A P 1, posterior B P 2, posterior C P 3, posterior D P 4, posterior E P 5, posterior (arrows indicating the presence of distal inner setae) F distal segment exopod of left P 5 (arrow indicating a trace of the distal inner seta). Scale bar: 100 µm." , "Figure 7. Boholina reducta sp. nov., allotype male. A rostrum and antennule, ventral view B P 5, posterior C P 5, anterior. Scale bars: 100 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466110" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466111" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466108" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466109" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466112" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466106" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466113" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/466107" .

